All Implemented Interfaces:
DependencyBuilder<MavenDependencyInfo>
public final class MavenDependencyProviderBuilder
extends Object
implements DependencyBuilder<MavenDependencyInfo>
Used to build a dependency provider that should be attached to a MavenDependencyLoader then loaded.
